## Proposed Changes

### Database Layer & API Enpoints

#### [MODIFY] [Job.js](file:///c:/Users/justi/Downloads/School%20Files/MainProjectCollection/ComprogStudies/ProjectsWebDev/Capstone%20Things/DeveloperVersion/backend/models/Job.js)
- Add a new field: `dateCompleted: { type: String, default: '' }` (stored as `YYYY-MM-DD` for consistency).

#### [MODIFY] [jobController.js](file:///c:/Users/justi/Downloads/School%20Files/MainProjectCollection/ComprogStudies/ProjectsWebDev/Capstone%20Things/DeveloperVersion/backend/controllers/jobController.js)
- **`setJobStatus`**: Instead of calling `findOneAndDelete` when `status === 'Completed'`, set `job.status = 'Completed'`, save `job.dateCompleted = todayStr`, and store `job.departure` time.
- **`getJobs`**: Modify query from `Job.find({})` to `Job.find({ status: { $ne: 'Completed' } })` to only fetch active queue items, keeping client updates and TV-mode quick.
- **`getAnalyticsData` [NEW]**: Create a new controller function that finds jobs by a given date range (or returns all if no range is specified), including completed ones.

#### [MODIFY] [jobRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/justi/Downloads/School%20Files/MainProjectCollection/ComprogStudies/ProjectsWebDev/Capstone%20Things/DeveloperVersion/backend/routes/jobRoutes.js)
- Register `router.get('/analytics', requireRole(['owner']), getAnalyticsData);` before other GET requests to secure the endpoint for owner access only.

